<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/50215695-roy-derousse"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_100x100-c7bfe730633c9983e27caaa66a8e244a.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/50215695-roy-derousse">Roy DeRousse</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">First of all, I do NOT recommend a chronological reading unless you&apos;ve already read the books in published order. I found two sources to help with a c<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">First of all, I do NOT recommend a chronological reading unless you've already read the books in published order. I found two sources to help with a chronological reading - Goodreads and Wikipedia:<br /><br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.goodreads.com/series/49339-pern-chronological-order">https://www.goodreads.com/series/4933...</a><br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Pern_books">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of...</a><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
