  <div class="friendReviews elementListBrown" >
    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2749086232" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2749086232" />
    <a title="Jerry" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5855981-jerry"><img alt="Jerry" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1520438201p2/5855981.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2749086232?book_show_action=true">Mar 13, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jerry" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jerry" href="/user/show/5855981-jerry">Jerry</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2749086232" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12818265117816056636">Books like this remind me of <i>Belle&apos;s Magical World</i>, the third entry in Disney&apos;s <i>Beauty and the Beast</i> trilogy.<br/><br/>However, that was never among my favorite House of Mouse productions, so, that isn&apos;t a good thing.<br/><br/>While each story in this collection was entertaining, I would have preferred an entire novel instead.</span>
  <span id="freeText12818265117816056636" style="display:none">Books like this remind me of <i>Belle's Magical World</i>, the third entry in Disney's <i>Beauty and the Beast</i> trilogy.<br /><br />However, that was never among my favorite House of Mouse productions, so, that isn't a good thing.<br /><br />While each story in this collection was entertaining, I would have preferred an entire novel instead.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12818265117816056636" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


