<span id="freeTextContainer12216725152967714903">A collection of short stories/novellas that expand on the early history of Pern. Some of the history is fun and a great display of McCaffrey&apos;s verdant imagination but a couple of the stories are overly long and not particularly interesting. This was a reread. I hadn&apos;t read it since first buying it years ago. It&apos;s not a bad book by any means but it will not retain a place in my permanent library.</span>
  <span id="freeText12216725152967714903" style="display:none">A collection of short stories/novellas that expand on the early history of Pern. Some of the history is fun and a great display of McCaffrey's verdant imagination but a couple of the stories are overly long and not particularly interesting. This was a reread. I hadn't read it since first buying it years ago. It's not a bad book by any means but it will not retain a place in my permanent library.</span>
