  <span id="freeText11331413496230465534" style="display:none">These five short stories that fill in the gaps of the early Pern years. The first story is the original survey team who came to Pern and declared it a planet worthy of settlement. Another story deals with the evacuation of Landing after the volcanic eruptions. Then there are stories about how the new settlements and weyrs are chosen in the North. The final story is about the rescue of a few settlers that didn't make it to the North but had been stuck in the south without dragon help during threadfall. I am not sure you would get much out of these stories if you weren't familiar with the overall story of Pern. </span>
