              <span id="reviewTextContainer1083638865" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7667725106353292756">Bunch of fun stories about a wonderful world. It ties a lot of the full novels together and answers some of the unanswered questions. Great book for Pern fans.</span>

